 keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">학기당</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px; text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">6</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">시간</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; width: 106px; height: 58px; border-width: 0.28pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: middle;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px; text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">저위험 학과</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; width: 385px; height: 58px; border-width: 0.28pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: middle;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수학과<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>통계학과<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>전자전기공학부<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>정보통신공학과<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>건축공학부<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>산업시스템공학과<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, AI</span>융합학부<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, AI</span>소프트웨어융합학부<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>가정교육과, 자율사물지능학과</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; width: 108px; height: 58px; border-top: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right: none; vertical-align: middle;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px; text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">년</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px; text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">3</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">시간</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; width: 598px; height: 40px; border-top: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1.7pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right: none; vertical-align: middle;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1) </span>고위험 : 위험물<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>화학물질<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>가스<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>실험장치 등<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span>을 사용하는 학과 및 연구기관</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">2) </span>저위험 : 고위험 학과를 제외한 학과 및 연구기관<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>컴퓨터 취급 연구 활동 등<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">  <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">사</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">기타사항</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">    1) </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">성적 반영 </span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">이</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">·</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">공 계열 학과 및 과목 일부 성적 반영</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">    2) </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">연구실안전관리위원회에서 정한 기준에 따라 제재를 부여할 수 있습니다.</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">    3) </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">문의사항 </span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">관리처 시설안전팀</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">내선번호 </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">☎</span>8569)</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">붙 임 </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: 1. </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">관련 법률 </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">부</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">         2. </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">온라인 이수 안내서 </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">부</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">끝</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"> </span></p>",
    "본문": "1.\n관련\n:\n연구실 안전환경 조성에 관한 법률 제\n20\n조\n(\n교육\n․\n훈련\n)\n2.\n상기 법에 의거하여\n, 2024\n학년도\n2\n학기 신규 및 정기 2차\n연구실 안전교육을 아래와 같이 시행하오니 기한 내 반드시 이수하여 주시기 바랍니다\n.\n가\n.\n교육명\n: 2024\n학년도\n2\n학기 신규 및 정기 2차 연구실 안전교육\n나\n.\n대상\n:\n이공계열 학부생\n,\n대학원생\n다\n.\n교육기간\n: 2024. 11. 1.(금\n) ~ 11. 30.(토\n)\n라\n.\n교육내용\n:\n연구실 안전법\n,\n화학\n,\n전기\n,\n소방\n,\n안전장비\n,\n연구실사고 등 그 밖에 안전관리에 관한 사항\n마\n.\n교육방법\n1) 신규교육 : 학과별 개별 집체교육\n2)\n정기교육\n:\n온라인교육\n-\n연구실안전교육시스템\n(https://edu.labs.go.kr)\n접속 후 원하는 교육 수강\n바\n.\n안전교육 이수시간\n대\n상\n구분\n관련학과\n비고\n신규\n전체\n신규 입학 대학원생\n,\n학부생\n⇒\n모든 학과 동일\n(\n구분 없음\n)\n입학 후\n3\n개월 이내\n2\n시간\n정기\n고위험 학과\n화학과\n,\n물리학과\n,\n건설환경공학과\n,\n화공생물공학과\n,\n기계로봇에너지공학과\n,\n에너지신소재공학과\n,\n시스템반도체학부, 미래전지융합공학과\n학기당\n6\n시간\n저위험 학과\n수학과\n,\n통계학과\n,\n전자전기공학부\n,\n정보통신공학과\n,\n건축공학부\n,\n산업시스템공학과\n, AI\n융합학부\n, AI\n소프트웨어융합학부\n,\n가정교육과, 자율사물지능학과\n1\n년\n3\n시간\n1)\n고위험 : 위험물\n(\n화학물질\n,\n가스\n,\n실험장치 등\n)\n을 사용하는 학과 및 연구기관\n2)\n저위험 : 고위험 학과를 제외한 학과 및 연구기관\n(\n컴퓨터 취급 연구 활동 등\n)\n사\n.\n기타사항\n1)\n성적 반영\n:\n이\n·\n공 계열 학과 및 과목 일부 성적 반영\n2)\n연구실안전관리위원회에서 정한 기준에 따라 제재를 부여할 수 있습니다.\n3)\n문의사항\n:\n관리처 시설안전팀\n(\n내선번호\n☎\n8569)\n붙 임\n: 1.\n관련 법률\n1\n부\n2.\n온라인 이수 안내서\n1\n부\n.\n끝\n.",
